Hello everybody,<br />
<br />
i'm creating a simple excel file with this great engine, and it works very well.<br />
Every row contains various data and one image image in a specific cell.<br />
<br />
I add the image using the simplest way to do that<br />
<pre><code>$objDrawing = new PHPExcel_Worksheet_Drawing();

$objDrawing-&gt;setName(&quot;name&quot;);
$objDrawing-&gt;setDescription(&quot;Description&quot;);
$objDrawing-&gt;setPath([...imagepath..]);
$objDrawing-&gt;setCoordinates('B' . $row);
$objDrawing-&gt;setWidthAndHeight(100, 100);
$objDrawing-&gt;setOffsetX(1);
$objDrawing-&gt;setWorksheet($spreadsheet-&gt;getActiveSheet());</code></pre>

As i said all works fine. The only things i want to know is:<br />
is it possible to let the image be sortable with the data in the same row? You know like the famous flag options on MS Excel &quot;Move but don't size/Move and size/etc..&quot;.<br />
I've read other discussions, but i didn't find answers about this.<br />
<br />
thank you!<br />
